\'93Catherine.\'94 We walked on a way and were stopped under a tree.\
\
\'93Say, \'91I\'92ve come back to Catherine in the night.\'92\'94\
\
\'93I\'92ve come back to Catherine in the night.\'94\
\
\'93Oh, darling, you have come back, haven\'92t you?\'94\
\
\'93Yes.\'94\
\
