\
\'93What horse is it?\'94\
\
\'93I don\'92t know. Mr. Meyers\'92 choice.\'94\
\
\'93Don\'92t you even know the name?\'94\
\
\'93No. You can find it on the programme. Number five I think.\'94\
\
\'93You have touching faith,\'94 she said. The number five won but did not pay\
