\
\'93Don\'92t you like it better when we\'92re alone?\'94\
\
\'93Yes,\'94 I said.\
\
\'93I felt very lonely when they were all there.\'94\
\
\'93It\'92s grand here,\'94 I said.\
\
\'93Yes. It\'92s really a pretty course.\'94\
\
\'93It\'92s nice.\'94\
\
\'93Don\'92t let me spoil your fun, darling. I\'92ll go back whenever you want.\'94\
\
\'93No,\'94 I said. \'93We\'92ll stay here and have our drink. Then we\'92ll go down\
and stand at the water jump for the steeplechase.\'94\
\
\'93You\'92re awfully good to me,\'94 she said.\
\
After we had been alone awhile we were glad to see the others again. We\
had a good time.\
