\
\'93Make a fire in the kitchen and dry your things,\'94 I said.\
\
\'93I don\'92t care about dry clothes,\'94 Piani said. \'93I want to sleep.\'94\
\
\'93I\'92m going to sleep on the major\'92s bed,\'94 Bonello said. \'93I\'92m going to\
