\'93You two sleep in there,\'94 I said. \'93I\'92ll wake you.\'94\
\
\'93The Austrians will wake us if you sleep too long, Tenente,\'94 Bonello\
said.\
\
\'93I won\'92t oversleep,\'94 I said. \'93Where\'92s Aymo?\'94\
\
\'93He went out in the kitchen.\'94\
\
\'93Get to sleep,\'94 I said.\
\
\'93I\'92ll sleep,\'94 Piani said. \'93I\'92ve been asleep sitting up all day. The\
