meat.\'94\
\
\'93This is better,\'94 he said. \'93Something hot will be good for those two\
anarchists. You go to sleep, Tenente.\'94\
\
\'93There\'92s a bed in the major\'92s room.\'94\
\
\'93You sleep there.\'94\
\
\'93No, I\'92m going up to my old room. Do you want a drink, Bartolomeo?\'94\
\
\'93When we go, Tenente. Now it wouldn\'92t do me any good.\'94\
\
\'93If you wake in three hours and I haven\'92t called you, wake me, will\
