\
\'93You are back. You are safe.\'94\
\
\'93Yes.\'94\
\
\'93Have you had breakfast?\'94\
\
\'93Yes.\'94\
\
\'93How are you, Tenente? How are you?\'94 the wife asked.\
\
\'93Fine.\'94\
\
\'93Won\'92t you have breakfast with us?\'94\
