\'93For you? The Italians wouldn\'92t let you out of the country.\'94\
\
\'93Yes. I know that. But the Swiss. What will they do?\'94\
\
\'93They intern you.\'94\
\
\'93I know. But what\'92s the mechanics of it?\'94\
\
\'93Nothing. It\'92s very simple. You can go anywhere. I think you just have\
