\
\'93I\'92d like to be there.\'94\
\
\'93You\'92re awfully polite. You aren\'92t in a bad mess, are you?\'94\
\
\'93I don\'92t know.\'94\
\
\'93Don\'92t tell me if you don\'92t want. How do you happen to be away from the\
