\'93I think I\'92m through with it.\'94\
\
\'93Good boy. I always knew you had sense. Can I help you any way?\'94\
\
\'93You\'92re awfully busy.\'94\
\
\'93Not a bit of it, my dear Henry. Not a bit of it. I\'92d be happy to do\
