\
I did not say anything.\
\
\'93You won\'92t say I can\'92t, will you?\'94\
\
\'93No. I think it would be exciting.\'94\
\
\'93Oh, you\'92re so sweet. And maybe I\'92d look lovely, darling, and be so thin\
and exciting to you and you\'92ll fall in love with me all over again.\'94\
\
\'93Hell,\'94 I said, \'93I love you enough now. What do you want to do? Ruin\
